Remarks
Meticulous 2009 Center Entrance Colonial with a two car attached garage set on beautifully landscaped lot with 3,783 sq. ft. of exquisitely appointed living space with crown molding, wainscoting and custom mill work, a Buderus heating system, an elegant two story Foyer, formal Living Room, formal Dining Room, 1st floor office, gorgeous vaulted ceiling Family Room with a gas fireplace and gourmet eat in Kitchen with large center island, Vikinig stainless steel appliances and a beautiful dining area with sliders to a large composite deck overlooking the fenced back yard. There are four spacious bedrooms including the lovely Master Bedroom Suite complete with sitting area, large walk in closet and luxurious full bathroom. The 3rd floor is waiting to be finished with existing rough plumbing and framing for 5th bedroom and full bath. Tremendous potential for additional living space in the lower level which has a rough finished game room. Steps to Harrington Elementary. OPEN HOUSE 2:30-4 PM!
